data.description: Walking into this home just gives you that family feeling. Built in 2006 this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home has 2 separate living areas, formal dining room, bar top overlooking kitchen, great closet space and a laundry area whose location really makes sense!! The screened lanai overlooks a large fenced backyard that's been landscaped nicely. Centrally located in Port St. Lucie, it's ez to get to I-95, the Turnpike and US1. You'll definitely want to call it YOUR Home Sweet Home!
